Longleaf Partners Funds Trust - Longleaf Partners International Fund: Private Company Information - Bloomberg









































  





















































































July 25, 2017 2:29 PM ET
Capital Markets

Company Overview of Longleaf Partners Funds Trust - Longleaf Partners International Fund



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Longleaf Partners Funds Trust - Longleaf Partners International Fund is an open ended equity mutual fund launched and managed by Southeastern Asset Management, Inc. The fund invests in the public equity markets of countries across the globe excluding the United States. It seeks to invest in stocks of companies operating across diversified sectors. The fund invests in value stocks of companies across all market capitalizations. It employs a combination of fundamental and quantitative analysis focusing on factors such as strong businesses which are understandable, financially sound, competitively entrenched, and generates growing free cash flow, good management partners who are capable operato...
Longleaf Partners Funds Trust - Longleaf Partners International Fund is an open ended equity mutual fund launched and managed by Southeastern Asset Management, Inc. The fund invests in the public equity markets of countries across the globe excluding the United States. It seeks to invest in stocks of companies operating across diversified sectors. The fund invests in value stocks of companies across all market capitalizations. It employs a combination of fundamental and quantitative analysis focusing on factors such as strong businesses which are understandable, financially sound, competitively entrenched, and generates growing free cash flow, good management partners who are capable operators, responsible capital allocators, trustworthy, and shareholder-oriented to create its portfolio. The fund benchmarks the performance of its portfolio against the MSCI EAFE Index. It employs in-house research to create its portfolio. Longleaf Partners Funds Trust - Longleaf Partners International Fund was formed on October 26, 1998 and is domiciled in the United States.
Detailed Description


6410 Poplar AvenueSuite 900Memphis, TN 38119-4843United StatesFounded in 1998



